#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.juk.metainfo.xml:7
msgid "JuK"
msgstr "JuK"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.juk.metainfo.xml:9
msgid "Music Player"
msgstr "Executor de musica"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.juk.metainfo.xml:11
msgid ""
"JuK is an audio jukebox application, supporting collections of MP3, Ogg "
"Vorbis, and FLAC audio files. It allows you to edit the \"tags\" of your "
"audio files, and manage your collection and playlists. Its main focus, in "
"fact, is on music management."
msgstr ""
"JuK es un application audio de jukebox application, supportante collectiones "
"de files audio MP3, Ogg Vorbis, e FLAC. Il permitte que tu modifica le "
"etiquettas \"tags\" de tu files audio, e gere tu collection e lista de "
"reproduction. Su focus principal de facto, es sur gestion de musica."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.juk.metainfo.xml:12
msgid "Features:"
msgstr "Characteristicas:"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.juk.metainfo.xml:14
msgid "Collection list and multiple user defined playlists"
msgstr ""
"Lista de collection e multiple listas de reproduction definite per le usator"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.juk.metainfo.xml:15
msgid ""
"Ability to scan directories to automatically import playlists and music "
"files on start up"
msgstr ""
"habilitate de scander directorios pro importar automaticamente listas de "
"reproduction e files de musica quando on initia"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.juk.metainfo.xml:16
msgid ""
"Dynamic Search Playlists that are automatically updated as fields in the "
"collection change"
msgstr ""
"Listas de reproduction de cerca dynamic que es automaticamente actualisate "
"como campos in le modification de collection"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.juk.metainfo.xml:17
msgid ""
"A Tree View mode where playlists are automatically generated for sets of "
"albums, artists and genres"
msgstr ""
"Un modo de vista a arbore ubi le listas de reproduction es generate "
"automaticamente pro insimul de albums, artistas e generes"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.juk.metainfo.xml:18
msgid "Playlist history to indicate which files have been played and when"
msgstr ""
"Chronologia de lista de reproduction per indicar qual files ha essite "
"reproducite e quando"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.juk.metainfo.xml:19
msgid "Inline search for filtering the list of visible items"
msgstr "cerca interne pro filtrar le lista de elementos visibile"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.juk.metainfo.xml:20
msgid "The ability to guess tag information based on the track's file name"
msgstr ""
"Le habilitate de conjecturar information de etiquetta basate sur le nomine "
"de file del tracia"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.juk.metainfo.xml:21
msgid "File renamer that can rename files based on the tag content"
msgstr ""
"Renominator de file que pote renominar files basate sur le contento de "
"etiquetta"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.juk.metainfo.xml:22
msgid ""
"Tag reading and editing support for many formats including ID3v1, ID3v2 and "
"Ogg Vorbis"
msgstr ""
"Supporto de modification e lectura de etiquetta per multe formatos "
"includente ID3v1, ID3v2 e Ogg Vorbis"
